{"tid":2491211,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"時隔一年　Oh My Girl 終於將在 5 月回歸！","createTime":"2021-04-16T06:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T11:41:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb25c4500bf6e8b9fc571211e4a8e3f0298d0924","tid":2491211,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_3e21b2eb37712824be3dac1b8e643331/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-16/134901-903404.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_3e21b2eb37712824be3dac1b8e643331%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-16%2F134901-903404.png&h=33e6fb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年以〈NONSTOP〉在獲得各界一致好評的 Oh My Girl，下個月終於要發行今年第一張專輯啦！<br />\n<br />\nWM Entertainment 今天（16 日）透露 Oh My Girl 將於 5 月 10 日帶著新專輯回歸，目前七人正在全力準備，消息一出立刻掀起熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_18144fd1036fc79551f97ec393046afe/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-16/134901-903403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_18144fd1036fc79551f97ec393046afe%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-16%2F134901-903403.jpg&h=40db961e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOh My Girl 去年 4 月以發行第七張迷你專輯〈NONSTOP〉，從預告階段就憑創意十足的概念獲得關注，發片後從同名主打歌到 &ldquo;Dolphin&rdquo; 等收錄曲都打入了音源榜，最受歡迎的這兩首歌也分別在今年 3、4 月獲得 Gaon Charrt 的白金認證，代表音源串流播放次數突破了一億次。<br />\n<br />\n上一次回歸時，Oh My Girl 寫下了出道以來的最佳首週專輯銷量成績，這一次她們又會帶來什麼樣的新歌呢？喜歡她們的話，最近一定要關注最新消息！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：WM Entertainment）"},{"pid":"90be8059eb58b100dd4414072dca4ce1de8c843e","tid":2491211,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"Who fking care!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829b1bbe4ef0c5b81cadd0ec5ec93188c980424b","tid":2491211,"uid":9309